{
  "chapter": 29,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲与徐子陵在彭城酒后，识破沈落雁的陷阱，拒绝前往倚红院。途中偶遇香玉山，获知翠碧楼所在。两人在旅店中意外觉醒提气轻身的能力，随后沈落雁持金簪突袭，寇仲与徐子陵联手以血战十式将其击退。沈落雁以闯关为赌约巧妙入房，劝降二人未果后威胁格杀。徐子陵凭才智推断沈落雁已知杨公宝藏之事。最终二人利用陈老谋所授建筑知识，借大汉双锤破壁逃入花园，施展鸟渡术脱身。本章展现了双龙武功突破与智勇兼备的成长。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "似乎有点不妥，那两人的对答来得太合时了，似还怕我们不知怎样到倚红院去，说得清楚无遗。\n\n照我看这两个定是沈落雁的人，见一计不成，又生一计。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你说得不错。\n\n既然李志会是沈落雁的人。这两个家伙也可能是她的人。\n\n唉！现在到那去好呢？还是先找处躲藏的地方为妙。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不去倚红改去倚绿好了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_lu_xing_ren",
      "text": "请问这位大叔，附近除倚红院外，还有那间是最有规模，最多漂亮姐儿的青楼呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你道是要问去那考科举吗？找青楼定要拣些二世祖模样，一眼看去便知是酒色过度的人来问才在行，看我的！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "text": "这位公子，在下有一事相询，请公子勿怪在下唐突。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "仁兄有话请说。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "text": "我两兄弟想知道这除倚红院外，还有那间青楼是最好的？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "是问对人了。\n\n我老爹正是开妓院的，就是在隔邻鸿园街的翠碧楼。论规模和姑娘，倚红院拍马都追不上。\n\n不过现在时候尚早，你们先去随处逛逛。到酉时才来。\n\n只要说是我香玉山的朋友，保证没有人敢侍候不周。仁兄请了，我还有要事去办呢。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "现在我甚么义军或官军都不想当了，杀了宇文化骨后，我们就专心赚钱，干我们的监货买卖，来就到青楼醉生梦死，快快乐乐过完这一生就算了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不是常说要建功立业吗？\n\n为何忽然又想要当个囤积投把的奸商？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "就算是奸商，我仲少都是最好的那一种奸商。\n\n难道见别人受苦受难，我们侠义之辈还会对他落井下石吗？\n\n不过坦白说，美人儿师傅说得对；现在我们何德何能，凭甚么去管别人的事。\n\n嘿！待我们武技大成时，练至甚么九玄大法第一百零八重境界，那时看到谁不顺眼，就一刀把他宰了，这就叫为民除害了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "世间那有这么简单如意的事，但不管怎样，也先要宰了宇文化骨那奸贼。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_niang",
      "speaker_name": "鸨娘",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "两位公子是否走错路了？\n\n那边才是倚红院的大门。我们刚开始营业，两位公子若是第一批客人，我们的红姐儿们定会特别用心侍候的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bao_niang",
      "text": "俏娘子你去告诉沈落雁那奸狡婆娘，当只会上一次，绝不会上第二次的。\n\n有种就来抓我们，不过着她别忘了她是朝廷重犯哩！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "快酉时了，我们就去做翠碧楼第一批的客人，说不定有半价的优待呢！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "喝酒就是有这种后遗症，若是沈婆娘派来的，我就要完蛋了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我是这世上最有责任心的人，否则谁来为把风。\n\n刚才有伙计来过问这问哪的，我偏不开门给他。哈！还有几个时辰沈婆娘就要输给我们了，不知秦老哥命运如何？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "待会先去东门看看有没有他留下来的暗记。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "还有别忘了我们曾答应李世民那小子的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我怎会忘了，那有钱的家伙不是说过东溟号明天才由洛阳回来吗？\n\n得趁今晚良辰美景，行乐及时啊！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "说来真好笑，以前在扬州时，到妓院门口看看都给人像乞丐般赶走，现在连妓院老板儿子的朵儿都任我们亮出来照宝。\n\n不过先作声明，我的初夜可不肯随便的，至少该有飘香院那恩将仇报的青青那种姿色才行。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "有钱自然有面有势，加上香玉山的朵儿撑腰，你陵少要那件就会有那件，包君满意，还不快翘屁股滚下床来？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "天！是怎么办到的，再来一趟好吗？怎么坐着也可提气的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "再试怕就不灵了，不若你自己试吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不是要赶着去逛窑子吗？还不快试试看？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "早试过十多吹了，连脚指都没有动。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我今次也不灵光了。唉！\n\n或者真该拜个大师傅，有难题时也好有个明师来指点。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "拜师傅有啥屁用，我们学的是《长生诀》上的怪功夫，天下无人通晓，只能靠自己去摸索。\n\n或者我们的问题是出在童男之身，故孤阳不长，破了身后便会立即武技大成。\n\n哈！定是这样了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "少说废话，还不先滚！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我滚！我滚！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tou_xi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "偷袭者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咦！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来得好！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "娘！我成功了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "美人儿军师。快滚进来挨刀。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "记着不可损我们半根毫毛，否则就算你输定了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "外面院子地方大些，你们出来再比比看。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "想叫手下围攻我们吗？哈｜知否我懂得狮子吼，大声一叫，保证彭城的总管大人都听得一清二楚。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不若这样好吗？\n\n假若我可闯关人房，就算我赢了。你两人乖乖归降。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "那是说你再没有把握活捉我们了，所以你已输了啦！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "怕她甚么，但却要有时间规限，我数十声你若过不了关，就算你输了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "就此一言为定。数吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "好了！\n\n我赢啦！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "这样输了是不会心服的，因为只像上趟般，利用了我们善良的本性。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你们除了用刀劈人外，便不懂其他制人的手法吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "我们并没有输，因为你虽入了房，却没有闯关，这个闯字是包含了动手的意思哩！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "大家坐下来谈谈好吗？\n\n唔！你两人现在看来顺眼多了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "有话快说，我们还要去逛窑子呢！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们知否窑子的姑娘都是身世可怜。\n\n你们恃着有几个子儿，就觉理所当然的去玩弄人家，究竟有没有感到惭愧？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "我倒没想过这点。但若没有人去光顾她们，她们赚不够赎身的银两，岂非更要一直凄凉下去吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "那所倚红院不是你们瓦岗军开的吗？为何却来数落我们？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "任何事物都是应需求而生，否则谁肯上战场去杀人又或送死呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你在说甚么？倚红院一向是杜伏威在这的眼线。\n\n干我们瓦岗军屁事。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们爱到青楼鬼混就去个够好了。现在秦叔宝已归降我军。\n\n你两个小子有甚么打算？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为何我们打得杀声震屋，仍没有人过来看看呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你像是忘了人家要活捉你们吗？外面已布下天罗地网，你两个小表插翼也难飞哩。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "你知否这叫恩将仇报？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "人家是为你们好才真。现在天下大乱，能拨乱反正者，只密公一人而已。\n\n我若非念着你们曾帮了我一个大忙，才没有情来劝你们加入我军呢。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "快作决定！我再没有时间浪费在你们身上了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "没时间就请自便吧！\n\n我两兄弟只爱海阔天空，自由自在。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "既不能为我所用，便须为我所杀，今天你们休想生离此处。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "怎样？\n\n就那么杀出去吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这样冲出去只是送死。说不定刚踏出门口，便有张罗网罩下来把我们呆子般擒着，我看她仍是想生擒我们。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "刚才我们闻老爹之名色变时，凭她的眼力才智，怎会看不出来而半句都不问，显是已知道我们的来历，所以才费尽心力要收服我们，好让我们心甘情愿献上杨公宝藏。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "小陵你真行。竟从她这么一个反应推断出这么多事来。\n\n哈！我有办法了。记得巨鲲帮陈老谋教过我们的建学吗？\n\n这旅馆是由八个四合院组成，我们位于东院的西厢位置，门口对着本院中间的花园，向门的墙外就是八院围成的主花园，大树三天，所以只要我们能窜到那去，逃生的机会就大多了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们又不是翟让，凭甚么破壁而逃呢？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若我猜得不错，上面定有敌人。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你给我把风，我先去弄松几块砖头。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 357
    }
